Resolution
ENROLLED HOUSE
JOINT
RESOLUTION NO. 1100 By: Kendrix of the House
and
Bergstrom of the Senate
A Joint Resolution approving certain Office of
Management and Enterprise Services proposed major
rule changes; and directing distribution.
SUBJECT: Office of Management and Enterprise Services rules
WHEREAS, pursuant to Section 308 of Title 75 of the Oklahoma
Statutes, the Oklahoma State Legislature shall adopt a separate
joint resolution to approve or disapprove major rules.
NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED BY THE HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES
AND THE SENATE OF THE 2ND SESSION OF THE 60TH OKLAHOMA LEGISLATURE:
SECTION 1. The Legislature hereby approves the following
proposed major rule changes submitted by the Office of Management
and Enterprise Services on or before February 1, 2026: OAC 260:75-
1-1; 260:75-1-2; 260:75-1-3; 260:75-1-4; 260:75-1-6; 260:75-1-7;
260:75-1-8; and 260:75-1-10.
SECTION 2. The Oklahoma Secretary of State is hereby directed
to distribute copies of this resolution to the Governor and the
editor of "The Oklahoma Register".

Passed the House of Representatives the 5th day of May, 2026.
Presiding Officer of the House
of Representatives
Passed the Senate the 14th day of May, 2026.
